            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the soup is cooking, tear the<strong> ciabatta<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into bite-sized pieces and add to a baking tray with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 7-8 min or until crisp and golden – these are your <strong>ciabatta croutons</strong></p>",
