    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are cooked through, remove the pot from the heat and discard the bay leaves</p><p>Add 3/4 of the <strong>crème fraîche</strong> (save the rest for later!) to the pot</p><p>Blitz until smooth with a <strong>(stick) blender </strong>and<strong> </strong>season with a generous pinch<strong> </strong>of<strong> salt </strong>–<strong> </strong>this is your<strong> crab bisque</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of boiled water if the soup is looking a little thick!</p>",
