    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crab bisque </strong>in bowls with a dollop of the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>crème fraîche </strong>over the top</p><p>Top with the <strong>ciabatta croutons </strong>and <strong>chopped chives</strong></p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
